Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小鎮發生了騷動 我們就走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還沒回來也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,騷動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後我們也找了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為她先回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,果然沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,把經過再詳細點告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,先通知一下阿修拉老師比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可隨時可能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在房間裡等她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝你 黛安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:07.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Take Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:12.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raise your hands!
